政」還是「執政」，需要商榷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年讀書俾佢教過都唔知佢紅底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"From wiki<br />\n有關對設立國民教育科的立場<br />\n何漢權曾表示國民教育科是將中國歷史科分件拆散，形同替中史「割脈」，更以「亡國論」形容相關香港教育制度改革。<br />\n<br />\n佢紅得黎又反國教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪因為驚自己教既中史地位不保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d840aed6777a692689e16cfb6f759c41d330ed","tid":633193,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"89309b9754ac785b0c1e1e3903fcf0b9d1d6926e","tid":633193,"uid":43173,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"想問吓中国除共產黨，仲有第二個黨執政？唔叫一黨專政叫乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"民進黨"},{"pid":"f35bf509c2083fdf3c8e466e702e94219310075c","tid":633193,"uid":46527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"中國唔係一黨專政<br />\n<br />\n只係咁啱當市委書記，高官被人革識嘅時候咁啱會彈多句「開除黨藉」，國家主席咁啱又係黨主席啫。全部都係咁啱，不要問，只要信。"},{"pid":"06c9593efb5e029e44d20710ae9659ec53fe97e3","tid":633193,"uid":8949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"我唔睇哩篇新聞都唔知共產黨係由八大民主黨共同管治<br />\n唔怪得中國冇民主啦"},{"pid":"4ff4ee7f4acfdbda8cae5d6258c08cb3a5498248","tid":633193,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>教育局反共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"affc573d08fa8fa632cc6c059d43ed88a540e582","tid":633193,"ui